[size=4]Description[/size]
If you refuse to start a new play through without giving a makeover to Irileth then this mod is for you. This mod gives a makeover to Irileth while staying true to her unique facial features. This mod makes Irileth easier on the eye, and gives her a new armor from the Witcher 2, because the Jarl of Whiterun can do much better. It also turns Irileth into a Nord, complimenting the Jarl.
